{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-7208d0cc-1ff6-421a-a76f-00095f4d30df-11\nfc_2263581c-906c-90d8-bebb-ed81d3ea397e_5","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/stores/README.md"},"result":{"success":{"content":"# Studio V2 · stores（一域一账本）\n\n> **真源：** [技术设计 21](../../../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/21-Studio客户端分层.md) · [规范改进需求](../../../../docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/规范改进需求.md) §3.1  \n> **门禁：** `STUDIO-STRUCT-021` / `022`（UI 禁直读；store 禁网络 / bis / ajaxProxy / `next/navigation`）\n\n## 约定\n\n```text\nsrc/stores/\n  studioV2Store.ts          # 壳层极薄偏好（workspace 标题等）；禁止扩业务切片\n  <domain>/                 # 一域一目录：characters / storyEditor / users / …\n    <domain>Store.ts        # Zustand；只结果型 write actions\n```\n\n| 域 | 目录 | 后续任务 |\n|----|------|----------|\n| 壳偏好 | 现 `studioV2Store.ts`（可迁 `shell/`） | 保持薄；不扩列表/选中 |\n| 故事编辑器 | `storyEditor/storyEditorStore.ts` | V2-LY-2 已落地；灌账/flush 见 V2-LY-3～4 |\n| 角色库 | `characters/` | V2-LY-5～6 |\n| 用户库 | `users/` | V2-LY-7 |\n| 资源库 | `assets/` | V2-LY-8 |\n| 包列表 | `packages/` | V2-LY-9 |\n| 调试器 | `debugger/` | V2-LY-10 |\n\n## 硬约束\n\n- **禁止**多域业务态塞进同一上帝 store。\n- store **不是** Profile / Memory / 磁盘包真源。\n- UI 经 feature bis 读写；shell bis 负责灌账。\n- 禁止本目录 `index.ts` barrel；直引具体文件。\n\n各域子目录 README 仅占位说明；真正 store 文件在对应 LY 任务落地。\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":33,"fileSize":1444,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/stores/README.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":33},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-7208d0cc-1ff6-421a-a76f-00095f4d30df-11\nfc_2263581c-906c-90d8-bebb-ed81d3ea397e_5","startedAtMs":"1784804027056","completedAtMs":"1784804027304"},"model_call_id":"c1257f6e-83db-456b-a7a9-7f8cce32a4eb-2-afd6","session_id":"cfef524f-82ae-40d6-8016-cf95181ea6e8","timestamp_ms":1784804027343}
